'''Tobias Menzies''' is a British actor, best known for his regular role as Brutus on the [[HBO]] series ''[[wikipedia:Rome (TV series)|Rome]]'' and as Andrew Lawrence on the BBC series ''[[wikipedia:Spooks|Spooks]]''.

In ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' he plays [[Edmure Tully]]. He was announced as a guest star in the [[Season 3|third season]] at San Diego Comic-Con 2012.&lt;ref name=ComicCon&gt;[http://www.westeros.org/GoT/News/Entry/Massive_Comic-Con_Casting_Reveals/ &quot;Massive Comic-Con Casting Reveals&quot; from Westeros.org, 13 July 2012]&lt;/ref&gt;

Menzies was cast in ''Rome'' by ''Game of Thrones'' casting director [[Nina Gold]]. He has also appeared in the films ''Finding Neverland'' (2004), ''Casino Royale'' (2006), ''Atonement'' (2007), and ''Forget Me Not'' (2010)
